doctor.name: Dr. Mohammad Azizur Rahman
doctor.specialty: Physical Medicine, Sports Injury & Rheumatology Specialist
doctor.info: Dr. Mohammad Azizur Rahman is a Physical Medicine Specialist in Mymensingh. His qualification is MBBS, BCS (Health), FCPS (Physical Medicine). He is a Assistant Professor, Physical Medicine & Rehabilitation at Mymensingh Medical College & Hospital. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Popular Diagnostic Center, Mymensingh. Practicing hour of Dr. Mohammad Azizur Rahman at Popular Diagnostic Center, Mymensingh is 4pm to 9pm (Closed: Thursday & Friday).

doctor.name: Dr. Md. Mahbubur Rahman
doctor.info: Dr. Md. Mahbubur Rahman is a Pain Specialist in Mymensingh. His qualification is MBBS (DMC), MSC (UK). He is a Consultant, Physical Medicine & Rehabilitation at TMC Diagnostic & Hospital, Mymensingh. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at TMC Diagnostic & Hospital, Mymensingh. Practicing hour of Dr. Md. Mahbubur Rahman at TMC Diagnostic & Hospital, Mymensingh is 10am to 8pm (Thu, Fri & Sat).
